metadata.description: A Portal to Adelaide is a living/dynamic NFT that uses real world weather data. APTA has 10 different artworks, 3 different modes of operation and operator controls for the owner. For the full experience visit associated app at arweave.net/P14em8RCt5Ua0ez45FIuMCA82e7o7EcaoYYmYaL4IjM
